id: pm-xc68
title: "As an organization running business workflows on pm, I can define roles and item-level policies (who may transition/approve what) enforced consistently at the SDK layer"
description: "Exploration story (spike + ADR only, parked at P4 like pm-is1a): principal-based item-level policy on top of the shipped per-type transition workflows — layered enforcement (SDK gate, validate/CI verification, git as the real trust boundary), honest about git-native bypass limits. Prerequisite thinking for the pm-8ngt companies-on-pm-SDK vision."
